==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: trial and error
<hw>tri"al and er"ror</hw> <def>The method of discovering something
desirable by trying many different things until one works; <as>as, the
traditional method of finding new drugs is by <ex>trial and
error</ex></as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><q>And millions miss for one that hits.</q>
<rj><qau>Swift.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Trial balance</ent>⟦br⟧
